                        <r3d:remarks>FDZ-BO (formerly: DSZ-BO) is a member of the RatSWD - research data - infrastructure; The quantitative data sets are available on demand as remote data processing and on-site. The transcripts are available on demand as Scientific Use file. The use is free.
